00:55:30.870 --> 00:55:33.900
But since many of the
things that you've said

00:55:33.900 --> 00:55:35.810
resonated with
myself, I felt like I

00:55:35.810 --> 00:55:38.240
need to stand up and
go and say something

00:55:38.240 --> 00:55:41.330
in defense of your points.

00:55:41.330 --> 00:55:42.260
Particularly one--

00:55:42.260 --> 00:55:44.030
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE].

00:55:44.030 --> 00:55:47.580
AUDIENCE: The information
of [? ability ?].

00:55:47.580 --> 00:55:50.570
The fact that we have access
to this vast, vast amount

00:55:50.570 --> 00:55:53.180
of information that enables
us to do things that normally

00:55:53.180 --> 00:55:54.440
would be difficult to do.

00:55:54.440 --> 00:55:58.300
Say, I'm a hardcore
do-it-yourselfer

00:55:58.300 --> 00:55:59.860
around my house.

00:55:59.860 --> 00:56:04.760
Having bought an old house,
having many things to fix,

00:56:04.760 --> 00:56:07.900
I think, displaced
many contractors.

00:56:07.900 --> 00:56:11.690
So, I did many things that I
never thought I would be doing.

00:56:11.690 --> 00:56:16.010
And not hiring other people
that maybe I would otherwise

00:56:16.010 --> 00:56:19.410
have hired because, first
of all, the information

00:56:19.410 --> 00:56:21.010
is available.

00:56:21.010 --> 00:56:22.780
I have access not
only to information.

00:56:22.780 --> 00:56:25.300
I have access to tools
that I can buy easily

00:56:25.300 --> 00:56:27.174
from online sources.

00:56:27.174 --> 00:56:28.840
Previously some of
these tools are maybe

00:56:28.840 --> 00:56:30.550
specialized, wouldn't
be so easy to build

00:56:30.550 --> 00:56:32.570
to buy and find locally.

00:56:32.570 --> 00:56:33.662
So that is easier.

00:56:33.662 --> 00:56:35.620
There is this aspect that
I also can relate to,

00:56:35.620 --> 00:56:38.590
the aspect of not wanting to
deal with some of those people,

00:56:38.590 --> 00:56:40.340
