with contractors

00:56:40.340 --> 00:56:44.870
while you are-- their actions
are often not that great.

00:56:44.870 --> 00:56:46.400
So, being able to avoid them.

00:56:46.400 --> 00:56:49.680
But I think the main
point is the fact

00:56:49.680 --> 00:56:54.380
that this information is
available, that is driving it,

00:56:54.380 --> 00:56:55.240
in my case.

00:56:55.240 --> 00:56:58.510
But what resonated about
it, I always question,

00:56:58.510 --> 00:57:00.430
is it worth the time
I'm putting into it?

00:57:00.430 --> 00:57:02.220
Losing my leisure time, maybe.

00:57:02.220 --> 00:57:07.460
Maybe spending the time just
relaxing, rather than working.

00:57:07.460 --> 00:57:08.620
So, there's that.

00:57:08.620 --> 00:57:09.911
CRAIG LAMBERT: Well, thank you.

00:57:09.911 --> 00:57:13.242
I mean, absolutely
it's a choice that you

00:57:13.242 --> 00:57:14.200
