up doing things.

00:57:41.280 --> 00:57:44.050
So, that can be a
legitimate choice,

00:57:44.050 --> 00:57:46.540
if that's the one
you want to make.

00:57:46.540 --> 00:57:48.812
That is leisure.

00:57:48.812 --> 00:57:49.728
Thanks for sharing it.

00:57:49.728 --> 00:57:50.936
AUDIENCE: It is and it isn't.

00:57:50.936 --> 00:57:51.997
This is the dilemma.

